he way from longbows to muskets and grenades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Trade with visiting merchants, convince them to join your settlement or plunder them if you wish!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Create caravans, travel the world by land or sea; discover new locations and establish new settlements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">PS: This game is in the same franchise as Grim Nights. However, <i>this game will focus less on tower defense and much more on your villagers and the management of your growing settlement</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(Also: This game was previously called 'Grim Nights 2'. Long story short: the name was changed because it is too different to easily be considered a sequel.)</p>","developers":["Edym Pixels"],"dlc":[2232050],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522280/header.jpg?t=1737101636","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"This game has been made by Mattias Myde, Edym Pixels \u00a9. It has been made with GameMaker Studio 2.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257089542,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257089542/movie480.mp4?t=1737024112","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257089542/movie_max.mp4?t=1737024112"},"name":"Grim Realms - Enhanced (1.1)","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257089542/b9ad962348a4974dd3988d3616db114c1ae29b0d/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1737024112","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257089542/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1737024112","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257089542/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1737024112"}}],"name":"Grim Realms","package_groups":[{"description":"","display_type":0,"is_recurring_subscription":